      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> Sklar-Quah war-skalds (Krojun's honor guard at the Acropolis travels three strong). One sings Inspired Rage while the others fight; the singer heals from range; any melee skald at ~30 HP falls back and swaps roles.</p><p><strong>Morale:</strong> they fight to the death <em>while Krojun lives</em>; if he falls, they quit the field and speak ill of the PCs (−1d6 Respect Points). <strong>Story award:</strong> if the PCs never attack the hot-heads, each thundercaller surviving the Acropolis pays XP as if defeated.</p>",
      "publication": {
